***** {{tact|below}}
**** {{topt|If I must.}}
***** {{tact|below}}
**** {{topt|No thanks, not this year.}}
***** {{tact|below}}
*** {{topt|Actually yes, I am rather cold.}}
**** '''Player:''' Actually yes, I am rather cold.
**** '''Duke Horacio:''' Well... I may be able to help there.
**** '''Duke Horacio:''' I wonder if you might help me with a little project of mine?
**** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
**** {{topt|Sure I can.}}
***** {{tact|below}}
**** {{topt|If I must.}}
***** {{tmissing}}
**** {{topt|No thanks, not this year.}}
***** {{tmissing}}
